  "title": "Junior Sales & Marketing (fresh-grads/ord welcomed! Fixed hours!)",
  "description": "<p>🚀 We’re Hiring: Sales Executive (Game Changer Wanted!)Are you the kind of person who loves a challenge, thrives on results, and gets a buzz from closing deals? Do you see opportunities where others see obstacles? If yes — we want YOU on our team!🌟 <br /><br />What You’ll Be Doing<br />•Build strong, lasting relationships with new and existing clients<br />•Identify opportunities, pitch solutions, and close deals like a pro<br />•Smash sales targets and celebrate wins with a high-energy team<br />•Collaborate with marketing and leadership to drive growth<br />•Represent our brand with confidence, passion, and professionalism<br /><br />🔥 What We’re Looking For\t<br />•\tA driven, ambitious go-getter with a winning mindset\t<br />•\tExcellent communication and negotiation skills\t•\tA hunger to learn, grow, and outperform expectations\t•\tSales experience is a plus — attitude and resilience are a must<br /><br />💎 What’s In It for You\t<br />•\tUncapped commissions\t<br />•\tFast career progression for top performers<br />•\tOngoing training, mentorship, and personal development\t<br />•\tA dynamic, supportive culture that celebrates success\t<br />•\tIncentives, rewards, and recognition for results🎯 <br /><br />Ready to Make an Impact?If you’re ready to take your sales career to the next level and be part of something exciting, apply now and let’s win together!</p>",
